{"tid":1158673,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"試過肛交真係返唔到轉頭","createTime":"2019-05-17T06:39:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-27T14:50:38.000Z","uid":431,"like":46,"dislike":220,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"cf5b8314a11b52130072f315baa80ffa8da3eb2d","tid":1158673,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T06:39:35.000Z","msg":"之前拍拖 同男朋友試過 但一唔係太痛就係整到我損咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />所以好抗拒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依兩年散咗有幾個sp 佢哋都想扑我後面 但我一直都拒絕因為有心理陰影<br />\n不過噚日其中一個話想試我咪應承咗佢囉～<br />\n我哋點玩就唔講啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我只係講下肛交嘅感覺～～～<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n嗰晚佢用咗一支有電嘅震震刺激我屎眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我本來有啲驚但因為無之前嗰啲痛法所以都俾佢震咗陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後佢就想入我後面～我本來都唔准嘅不過佢幾溫柔又氹我我咪俾佢慢慢入囉～～<br />\n真係好奇怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢其實唔算細size 但只係有少少痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n都算頂得順 所以我允許佢繼續因為感覺太刺激<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n後尾佢一邊插我後面又玩我前面 當場成個人覺得好充實<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n完事之後我發覺我屎眼無損無流血<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔知點解突然唔怕肛交 仲好想再試多一次添！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44fb8c09fdd684dd903eeff8c22cfe654b756e56","tid":1158673,"uid":212990,"like":121,"dislike":5,"score":116,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T06:40:31.000Z","msg":"noted with thanks."},{"pid":"11fab3cf3fd08c09887623b2c16a446aff944896","tid":1158673,"uid":35105,"like":295,"dislike":2,"score":293,"citedBy":1,"replyTime"